# в”Җв”Җ н•ңкөӯ мҰқмӢң нңҙмһҘмқј мһҗлҸҷ кҙҖлҰ¬ в”Җв”Җ
# KRX кіөкіөлҚ°мқҙн„° APIлЎң л§Өл…„ мһҗлҸҷ к°ұмӢ 
_kr_holidays: set = set()
_holiday_loaded_year: int = 0

def _load_kr_holidays(year: int = None):
    """
    кіөкіөлҚ°мқҙн„°нҸ¬н„ё KRX нңҙмһҘмқј APIлЎң мһҗлҸҷ мЎ°нҡҢ
    API мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң н•ҳл“ңмҪ”л”© fallback мӮ¬мҡ©
    """
    global _kr_holidays, _holiday_loaded_year
    if year is None:
        year = datetime.now().year
    if _holiday_loaded_year == year and _kr_holidays:
        return

    # 1м°Ё: кіөкіөлҚ°мқҙн„°нҸ¬н„ё н•ңкөӯмІңл¬ём—°кө¬мӣҗ нҠ№мқј м •ліҙ API
    loaded = False
    pub_api_key = os.environ.get("PUBLIC_DATA_API_KEY", "")
    if pub_api_key:
        try:
            resp = requests.get(
                "http://apis.data.go.kr/B090041/openapi/service/SpcdeInfoService/getRestDeInfo",
                params={"serviceKey": pub_api_key, "solYear": year,
                        "numOfRows": 50, "_type": "json"},
                timeout=10
            )
            items = resp.json().get("response",{}).get("body",{}).get("items",{}).get("item",[])
            if isinstance(items, dict): items = [items]
            holidays = {str(i["locdate"]) for i in items if i.get("locdate")}
            if holidays:
                _kr_holidays = holidays
                _holiday_loaded_year = year
                loaded = True
                print(f"  рҹ“… кіөнңҙмқј {len(holidays)}мқј мһҗлҸҷ лЎңл“ң ({year}л…„)")
        except Exception as e:
            print(f"  вҡ пёҸ кіөнңҙмқј API мӢӨнҢЁ: {e}")

    # 2м°Ё: KRX мһҘмҡҙмҳҒмқјм • мҠӨнҒ¬лһҳн•‘ fallback
    if not loaded:
        try:
            resp = requests.post(
                "http://open.krx.co.kr/contents/OPN/99/OPN99000001.jspx",
                data={"tboxisuCd_finder_secuprod0_0":"","isu_cd":"",
                      "isuCd":"","isu_nm":"","searchType":"1",
                      "strtDd": f"{year}0101","endDd": f"{year}1231",
                      "pagePath":"/contents/COM/GenerateOTP.jspx"},
                timeout=10
            )
            # к°„лӢЁ нҢҢмӢұ (мӢӨнҢЁн•ҙлҸ„ кҙңм°®мқҢ)
        except Exception: pass

    # 3м°Ё: н•ҳл“ңмҪ”л”© fallback (API лӘЁл‘җ мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң)
    if not loaded:
        fallback = {
            2025: {"20250101","20250128","20250129","20250130","20250301",
                   "20250505","20250506","20250603","20250606","20250815",
                   "20251003","20251008","20251009","20251225"},
            2026: {"20260101","20260127","20260128","20260129","20260301",
                   "20260505","20260525","20260606","20260815",
                   "20261002","20261003","20261005","20261009","20261225","20261231"},
        }
        _kr_holidays = fallback.get(year, set())
        _holiday_loaded_year = year
        print(f"  рҹ“… кіөнңҙмқј fallback мӮ¬мҡ© ({year}л…„, {len(_kr_holidays)}мқј)")

def is_holiday(date_str: str = None) -> bool:
    """мЈјл§җ лҳҗлҠ” кіөнңҙмқј м—¬л¶Җ"""
    now = datetime.strptime(date_str, "%Y%m%d") if date_str else datetime.now()
    _load_kr_holidays(now.year)
    return now.weekday() >= 5 or now.strftime("%Y%m%d") in _kr_holidays

def is_market_open() -> bool:
    now = datetime.now()
    if is_holiday(): return False
    return dtime(9, 0) <= now.time() <= dtime(15, 30)

def is_any_market_open() -> bool:
    """
    KRX лҳҗлҠ” NXT мӨ‘ н•ҳлӮҳлқјлҸ„ м—ҙл Ө мһҲмңјл©ҙ True
    мҪ”л“ң м „л°ҳм—җм„ң 'мһҘмқҙ мҷ„м „нһҲ лҒқлӮ¬лҠ”к°Җ'лҘј нҢҗлӢЁн•  л•Ң мӮ¬мҡ©
    - KRX: 09:00~15:30
    - NXT: 08:00~20:00
    """
    return is_market_open() or is_nxt_open()

def is_nxt_listed(code: str) -> bool:
    """
    н•ҙлӢ№ мў…лӘ©мқҙ NXTм—җ мғҒмһҘлҸј мһҲлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқё
    _nxt_unavailableм—җ м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ мғҒмһҘлҗң кІғмңјлЎң к°„мЈј (мЎ°нҡҢ мӢң мһҗлҸҷ нҢҗлі„)
    """
    return code not in _nxt_unavailable

def minutes_since(dt: datetime) -> int:
    return int((datetime.now() - dt).total_seconds() // 60)

def is_strict_time() -> bool:
    """v40.0: KRX + NXT мһҘ мҙҲл°ҳ/нӣ„л°ҳ м—„кІ© мӢңк°„лҢҖ нҢҗлі„
    v40.0-#8: 14:30 мқҙнӣ„ + кёҲмҡ”мқј 14:00 мқҙнӣ„ м¶”к°Җ м—„кІ© нҢҗм •
    """
    now = datetime.now()
    n   = now.time()
    # KRX мһҘ мҙҲл°ҳ/нӣ„л°ҳ
    o_e = (now.replace(hour=9,  minute=0)  + timedelta(minutes=STRICT_OPEN_MINUTES)).time()
    c_s = (now.replace(hour=15, minute=30) - timedelta(minutes=STRICT_CLOSE_MINUTES)).time()
    if dtime(9, 0) <= n <= o_e or n >= c_s:
        return True
    # v40.0-#8: мһҘ нӣ„л°ҳ 14:30 мқҙнӣ„ вҶ’ м—„кІ© (л§Ҳк°җ л§Өл¬ј / ліҖлҸҷм„ұ нҷ•лҢҖ)
    if n >= dtime(14, 30):
        return True
    # v40.0-#8: кёҲмҡ”мқј 14:00 мқҙнӣ„ вҶ’ м—„кІ© (мЈјл§җ мҳӨлІ„лӮҳмқҙнҠё лҰ¬мҠӨнҒ¬)
    if now.weekday() == 4 and n >= dtime(14, 0):
        return True
    # NXT мһҘм „ мҙҲл°ҳ (08:00~08:10) + мһҘнӣ„л°ҳ (19:50~20:00)
    if n <= dtime(8, STRICT_OPEN_MINUTES):
        return is_nxt_open()  # NXT м—ҙл ӨмһҲмқ„ л•Ңл§Ң
    if dtime(19, 50) <= n <= dtime(20, 0):
        return True
    return False


def _get_time_risk_profile() -> str:
    """v40.0-#6: нҳ„мһ¬ мӢңк°„лҢҖмқҳ лҰ¬мҠӨнҒ¬ н”„лЎңнҢҢмқј л°ҳнҷҳ.
    мһҘмӨ‘(normal) / кёҲмҡ”мқјл§Ҳк°җм „(friday_close) / м•јк°„мһҘм „(pre_open)
    """
    now = datetime.now()
    n = now.time()
    # м•јк°„В·мһҘм „ (20:00 ~ 08:59)
    if n >= dtime(20, 0) or n < dtime(9, 0):
        return "pre_open"
    # кёҲмҡ”мқј 14:00 мқҙнӣ„
    if now.weekday() == 4 and n >= dtime(14, 0):
        return "friday_close"
    # мқјл°ҳ мһҘмӨ‘
    return "normal"

# ============================================================
# рҹ”җ KIS API
# ============================================================
def _wait_for_kis_rest_slot(kind: str = "rest") -> None:
    """мӢӨм „ KIS REST burstлҘј 1мҙҲ мңҲлҸ„мҡ° лӮҙл¶Җ мғҒн•ңмңјлЎң нҸүнғ„нҷ”н•ңлӢӨ."""
    limit = KIS_TOKEN_LIMIT_PER_SEC if kind == "token" else KIS_REST_LIMIT_PER_SEC
    limit = max(1, int(limit or 1))
    window = 1.0
    min_sleep = 0.01
    dq = _kis_token_call_times if kind == "token" else _kis_rest_call_times
    stat_wait_key = "token_wait_sec" if kind == "token" else "rest_wait_sec"
    stat_evt_key = "token_wait_events" if kind == "token" else "rest_wait_events"

    while True:
        sleep_for = 0.0
        with _kis_rate_lock:
            now = time.monotonic()
            while dq and now - dq[0] >= window:
                dq.popleft()
            if len(dq) < limit:
                dq.append(now)
                return
            oldest = dq[0] if dq else now
            sleep_for = max(min_sleep, window - (now - oldest) + 0.005)
            _kis_rate_stats[stat_evt_key] = int(_kis_rate_stats.get(stat_evt_key, 0)) + 1
            _kis_rate_stats[stat_wait_key] = float(_kis_rate_stats.get(stat_wait_key, 0.0)) + float(sleep_for)
        time.sleep(sleep_for)

def get_token(retry: int = 3) -> str:
    global _access_token, _token_expires
    if _access_token and time.time() < _token_expires:
        return _access_token
    for attempt in range(retry):
        try:
            _wait_for_kis_rest_slot("token")
            resp = _session.post(f"{KIS_BASE_URL}/oauth2/tokenP",
                json={"grant_type":"client_credentials","appkey":KIS_APP_KEY,"appsecret":KIS_APP_SECRET},
                timeout=15)
            resp.raise_for_status()
            d = resp.json()
            _access_token  = d["access_token"]
            _token_expires = time.time() + int(d.get("expires_in", 86400)) - 300
            print(f"вң… KIS нҶ нҒ° л°ңкёү ({datetime.now().strftime('%H:%M:%S')})")
            return _access_token
        except Exception as e:
            _log_error(f"get_token(attempt={attempt+1})", e, critical=attempt==2); time.sleep(5*(attempt+1))
    raise Exception("вқҢ KIS нҶ нҒ° мөңмў… мӢӨнҢЁ")

def _headers(tr_id: str) -> dict:
    return {"Content-Type":"application/json; charset=utf-8",
            "Authorization":f"Bearer {get_token()}",
            "appkey":KIS_APP_KEY,"appsecret":KIS_APP_SECRET,
            "tr_id":tr_id,"custtype":"P"}


def _safe_get(url: str, tr_id: str, params: dict, *, return_meta: bool = False):
    """v38.3-P1-8: KIS GET with retry/backoff. Never raises.
    return_meta=True вҶ’ (data, status, ct, body_snippet) 4-tuple.
    return_meta=False(кё°ліё) вҶ’ dictл§Ң л°ҳнҷҳ.
    """
    last_exc = None; last_status = None; last_ct = ""; last_body_snip = ""; last_url = url

    for attempt in range(3):
        try:
            _wait_for_kis_rest_slot("rest")
            resp = _session.get(url, headers=_headers(tr_id), params=params, timeout=15)
            last_status = getattr(resp, "status_code", None)
            last_ct = ((getattr(resp, "headers", {}) or {}).get("Content-Type", "") or "")
            last_url = getattr(resp, "url", url) or url

            if last_status == 403:
                global _access_token
                _access_token = None
                _wait_for_kis_rest_slot("rest")
                resp = _session.get(url, headers=_headers(tr_id), params=params, timeout=15)
                last_status = getattr(resp, "status_code", None)
                last_ct = ((getattr(resp, "headers", {}) or {}).get("Content-Type", "") or "")
                last_url = getattr(resp, "url", url) or url

            if last_status == 200:
                data = safe_json_response(resp)
                return (data, last_status, last_ct, "") if return_meta else data

            try:
                raw = (getattr(resp, "text", "") or "").strip()
                last_body_snip = " ".join(raw.split())[:200]
            except Exception:
                last_body_snip = ""

            if return_meta:
                break

            j = safe_json_response(resp)
            if isinstance(j, dict) and j:
                msg_cd = j.get("msg_cd") or j.get("error_code") or j.get("code")
                msg1 = j.get("msg1") or j.get("message") or j.get("error_description") or j.get("error")
                last_exc = f"rt_cd={j.get('rt_cd')} msg_cd={msg_cd} msg={msg1}"
            else:
                last_exc = None
        except Exception as e:
            last_exc = e
        try:
            time.sleep(0.8 * (2 ** attempt))
        except Exception:
            pass

    try:
        if last_status == 404 and isinstance(last_url, str):
            if "chgrate-pcls-100" in last_url: _disable_rank_api_for_today("404")
            if "inquire-daily-trade" in last_url: _disable_daily_trade_api_for_today("404")
    except Exception:
        pass
    try:
        print(f"вҡ пёҸ API мҳӨлҘҳ ({tr_id}): url={last_url} status={last_status} ct={last_ct} err={last_exc} body={last_body_snip}")
    except Exception:
        pass
    return ({}, last_status, last_ct, last_body_snip) if return_meta else {}

def _safe_get_meta(url: str, tr_id: str, params: dict):
    """v38.3: _safe_get лһҳнҚј (н•ҳмң„ нҳёнҷҳ)"""
    return _safe_get(url, tr_id, params, return_meta=True)

# ============================================================
# рҹ“Ҡ мқјлҙү лҚ°мқҙн„° (кіөнҶө мӮ¬мҡ©)
# ============================================================
_daily_cache = {}  # code вҶ’ {items, ts}
_atr_cache   = {}  # code вҶ’ {atr, date}  н•ҳлЈЁ 1нҡҢ к°ұмӢ 

def get_daily_data(code: str, days: int = 60) -> list:
    """мқјлҙү лҚ°мқҙн„° мЎ°нҡҢ (мәҗмӢң 30л¶„)"""
    cached = _daily_cache.get(code)
    if cached and time.time() - cached["ts"] < 1800:
        return cached["items"]
    try:
        end   = datetime.now().strftime("%Y%m%d")
        start = (datetime.now() - timedelta(days=days+10)).strftime("%Y%m%d")
        url   = f"{KIS_BASE_URL}/uapi/domestic-stock/v1/quotations/inquire-daily-itemchartprice"
        params = {"FID_COND_MRKT_DIV_CODE":"J","FID_INPUT_ISCD":code,
                  "FID_INPUT_DATE_1":start,"FID_INPUT_DATE_2":end,
                  "FID_PERIOD_DIV_CODE":"D","FID_ORG_ADJ_PRC":"0"}
        resp_json = _safe_get(url, "FHKST03010100", params)
        items = resp_json.get("output2", []) if isinstance(resp_json, dict) else []
        items = sorted([{
            "date":  i.get("stck_bsop_date",""),
            "open":  int(i.get("stck_oprc",0)),
            "high":  int(i.get("stck_hgpr",0)),
            "low":   int(i.get("stck_lwpr",0)),
            "close": int(i.get("stck_clpr",0)),
            "vol":   int(i.get("acml_vol",0)),
        } for i in items if i.get("stck_bsop_date")], key=lambda x: x["date"])
        _daily_cache[code] = {"items": items, "ts": time.time()}
        return items
    except Exception as e:
        _log_error(f"get_daily_data({code})", e); return []

# ============================================================
# в‘Ұ-A ліҙмЎ°м§Җн‘ң кі„мӮ° (RSI / мқҙлҸҷнҸүк·  / ліјлҰ°м Җл°ҙл“ң / мң мӮ¬нҢЁн„ҙ)
# ============================================================

def calc_rsi(items: list, period: int = None) -> float:
    """
    RSI кі„мӮ°. periodлҠ” _dynamic["rsi_period"] мһҗлҸҷ м Ғмҡ©.
    л°ҳнҷҳ: 0~100 (70вҶ‘ кіјл§ӨмҲҳ, 30вҶ“ кіјл§ӨлҸ„)
    """
    period = period or int(_dynamic.get("rsi_period", 14))
    closes = [i["close"] for i in items if i.get("close")]
    if len(closes) < period + 1:
        return 50.0  # лҚ°мқҙн„° л¶ҖмЎұ мӢң мӨ‘лҰҪк°’
    gains, losses = [], []
    for i in range(1, period + 1):
        diff = closes[-(period + 1 - i)] - closes[-(period + 2 - i)]
        (gains if diff > 0 else losses).append(abs(diff))
    avg_gain = sum(gains) / period if gains else 0
    avg_loss = sum(losses) / period if losses else 0
    if avg_loss == 0:
        return 100.0
    rs = avg_gain / avg_loss
    return round(100 - (100 / (1 + rs)), 1)

def calc_ma_trend(items: list) -> dict:
    """
    мқҙлҸҷнҸүк· м„  м •л°°м—ҙ м—¬л¶Җ нҷ•мқё.
    _dynamic["ma_short"/"ma_mid"/"ma_long"] мһҗлҸҷ м Ғмҡ©.
    л°ҳнҷҳ: {"aligned": bool, "short": float, "mid": float, "long": float, "desc": str}
    """
    s = int(_dynamic.get("ma_short", 5))
    m = int(_dynamic.get("ma_mid",   20))
    l = int(_dynamic.get("ma_long",  60))
    closes = [i["close"] for i in items if i.get("close")]
    if len(closes) < l:
        return {"aligned": None, "short": 0, "mid": 0, "long": 0, "desc": "лҚ°мқҙн„°л¶ҖмЎұ"}
    ma_s = sum(closes[-s:]) / s
    ma_m = sum(closes[-m:]) / m
    ma_l = sum(closes[-l:]) / l
    aligned   = ma_s > ma_m               # v41.83: м •л°°м—ҙ кё°мӨҖ мҷ„нҷ” (5мқјм„  > 20мқјм„ )
    partially = (ma_s > ma_m) or (ma_m > ma_l)
    if aligned:
        desc = f"вң… м •л°°м—ҙ ({s}>{m}мқј)"
    elif partially:
        desc = f"рҹҹЎ л¶Җл¶„м •л°°м—ҙ"
    else:
        desc = f"рҹ”ө м—ӯл°°м—ҙ"
    return {"aligned": aligned, "partial": partially,
            "short": round(ma_s), "mid": round(ma_m), "long": round(ma_l), "desc": desc}

def calc_bollinger(items: list, period: int = None, k: float = 2.0) -> dict:
    """
    ліјлҰ°м Җл°ҙл“ң кі„мӮ°.
    л°ҳнҷҳ: {"upper": int, "mid": int, "lower": int,
           "pct_b": float,  # нҳ„мһ¬к°Җк°Җ л°ҙл“ң лӮҙ мң„м№ҳ (0=н•ҳлӢЁ, 1=мғҒлӢЁ)
           "breakout": bool, "desc": str}
    """
    period = period or int(_dynamic.get("bb_period", 20))
    closes = [i["close"] for i in items if i.get("close")]
    if len(closes) < period:
        return {"upper": 0, "mid": 0, "lower": 0, "pct_b": 0.5, "breakout": False, "desc": "лҚ°мқҙн„°л¶ҖмЎұ"}
    window = closes[-period:]
    mid    = sum(window) / period
    std    = (sum((c - mid) ** 2 for c in window) / period) ** 0.5
    upper  = int(mid + k * std)
    lower  = int(mid - k * std)
    cur    = closes[-1]
    pct_b  = round((cur - lower) / (upper - lower), 2) if upper != lower else 0.5
    breakout = cur >= upper
    if breakout:
        desc = f"рҹҡҖ мғҒлӢЁ лҸҢнҢҢ (л°ҙл“ңнҸӯ {(upper-lower)/mid*100:.1f}%)"
    elif pct_b >= 0.8:
        desc = f"рҹ”Ҙ мғҒлӢЁ к·јм ‘ ({pct_b*100:.0f}%)"
    elif pct_b <= 0.2:
        desc = f"рҹҺҜ н•ҳлӢЁ к·јм ‘ ({pct_b*100:.0f}%) вҖ” л°ҳл“ұ к°ҖлҠҘ"
    else:
        desc = f"л°ҙл“ң мӨ‘к°„ ({pct_b*100:.0f}%)"
    return {"upper": upper, "mid": int(mid), "lower": lower,
            "pct_b": pct_b, "breakout": breakout, "desc": desc}

def calc_indicators(code: str) -> dict:
    """
    RSI + MA + ліјлҰ°м Җл°ҙл“ң н•ң лІҲм—җ кі„мӮ°.
    get_daily_data мәҗмӢң нҷңмҡ© вҶ’ API м¶”к°Җ нҳём¶ң м—ҶмқҢ.
    л°ҳнҷҳ: {"rsi": float, "ma": dict, "bb": dict, "filter_pass": bool, "score_adj": int, "summary": str}
    """
    try:
        items = get_daily_data(code, 70)
        if len(items) < 20:
            return {"rsi": 50, "ma": {}, "bb": {}, "filter_pass": True, "score_adj": 0, "summary": ""}

        rsi = calc_rsi(items)
        ma  = calc_ma_trend(items)
        bb  = calc_bollinger(items)

        score_adj   = 0
        filter_pass = True
        reasons     = []

        # в”Җв”Җ кё°лҠҘлі„ к°ҖмӨ‘м№ҳ м Ғмҡ© в”Җв”Җ
        w_rsi = _dynamic.get("feat_w_rsi", 1.0)
        w_ma  = _dynamic.get("feat_w_ma",  1.0)
        w_bb  = _dynamic.get("feat_w_bb",  1.0)

        # в”Җв”Җ RSI н•„н„° вҶ’ v38.6: м°ЁлӢЁ м ңкұ°, к°җм җл§Ң (мһҗкёҲмң мһ… мў…лӘ©мқ„ RSIлЎң лҶ“м№ҳм§Җ м•ҠмқҢ) в”Җв”Җ
        rsi_overbuy  = float(_dynamic.get("rsi_overbuy",  70))
        rsi_oversell = float(_dynamic.get("rsi_oversell", 30))
        if w_rsi > 0:
            if rsi >= rsi_overbuy:
                score_adj   -= int(15 * w_rsi)
                reasons.append(f"вҡ пёҸ RSI {rsi:.0f} кіјл§ӨмҲҳ -{int(15*w_rsi)}м җ (к°җм җл§Ң, м°ЁлӢЁX)")
            elif rsi <= rsi_oversell:
                score_adj += int(10 * w_rsi)
                reasons.append(f"рҹҺҜ RSI {rsi:.0f} кіјл§ӨлҸ„ +{int(10*w_rsi)}м җ")
            elif rsi >= 60:
                score_adj += int(5 * w_rsi)
                reasons.append(f"рҹ“Ҡ RSI {rsi:.0f} к°•м„ё +{int(5*w_rsi)}м җ")

        # в”Җв”Җ мқҙлҸҷнҸүк·  н•„н„° вҶ’ v38.6: м°ЁлӢЁ м ңкұ°, к°җм җл§Ң в”Җв”Җ
        if w_ma > 0:
            if ma.get("aligned") is False and not ma.get("partial"):
                score_adj -= int(10 * w_ma)
                reasons.append(f"вҡ пёҸ {ma.get('desc','м—ӯл°°м—ҙ')} -{int(10*w_ma)}м җ (к°җм җл§Ң)")
            elif ma.get("aligned"):
                score_adj += int(10 * w_ma)
                reasons.append(f"вң… {ma.get('desc','м •л°°м—ҙ')} +{int(10*w_ma)}м җ")
            elif ma.get("partial"):
                score_adj += int(3 * w_ma)
                reasons.append(f"рҹҹЎ л¶Җл¶„м •л°°м—ҙ +{int(3*w_ma)}м җ")

        # в”Җв”Җ ліјлҰ°м Җл°ҙл“ң н•„н„° в”Җв”Җ
        if w_bb > 0:
            if bb.get("breakout"):
                score_adj += int(15 * w_bb)
                reasons.append(f"рҹҡҖ ліјлҰ°м Җ мғҒлӢЁ лҸҢнҢҢ +{int(15*w_bb)}м җ")
            elif bb.get("pct_b", 0.5) <= 0.2:
                score_adj += int(8 * w_bb)
                reasons.append(f"рҹҺҜ ліјлҰ°м Җ н•ҳлӢЁ к·јм ‘ +{int(8*w_bb)}м җ")

        summary = "\n".join(reasons) if reasons else ""
        return {"rsi": rsi, "ma": ma, "bb": bb,
                "filter_pass": filter_pass, "score_adj": score_adj, "summary": summary}
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"  вҡ пёҸ м§Җн‘ң кі„мӮ° мҳӨлҘҳ ({code}): {e}")
        return {"rsi": 50, "ma": {}, "bb": {}, "filter_pass": True, "score_adj": 0, "summary": ""}

# в”Җв”Җ мң мӮ¬ нҢЁн„ҙ л§Өм№ӯ (signal_log кё°л°ҳ) в”Җв”Җ
def _get_similar_pattern_stats(code: str, signal_type: str, change_rate: float, vol_ratio: float) -> dict:
    """мң мӮ¬нҢЁн„ҙ нҶөкі„ кіөнҶө кі„мӮ° (мғҒм„ё н‘ңмӢң / мҡ”м•Ҫ н‘ңмӢң / лӮҙл¶Җ м җмҲҳнҷ” кіөмҡ©)."""
    try:
        data = _load_signal_history()
        completed = _get_completed_signals(data)
        if len(completed) < 3:
            return {}

        out = {"same_stock": {}, "similar": {}, "primary": {}}

        same_stock = [v for v in completed if v.get("code") == code]
        if len(same_stock) >= 2:
            s_wins = sum(1 for v in same_stock if v.get("pnl_pct", 0) > 0)
            s_wr = round(s_wins / len(same_stock) * 100)
            s_avg = round(sum(v.get("pnl_pct", 0) for v in same_stock) / len(same_stock), 1)
            s_best = max(same_stock, key=lambda x: x.get("pnl_pct", 0))
            s_worst = min(same_stock, key=lambda x: x.get("pnl_pct", 0))
            out["same_stock"] = {
                "label": "лҸҷмқј мў…лӘ©",
                "count": len(same_stock),
                "win_rate": s_wr,
                "avg_pnl": s_avg,
                "best_pnl": round(float(s_best.get("pnl_pct", 0) or 0), 1),
                "worst_pnl": round(float(s_worst.get("pnl_pct", 0) or 0), 1),
                "name": same_stock[0].get("name", code),
            }

        same_type = [v for v in completed if v.get("signal_type") == signal_type]
        if len(same_type) >= 3:
            similar = [v for v in same_type
                       if abs(float(v.get("change_at_detect", 0) or 0) - float(change_rate or 0)) <= 3.0
                       and abs(float(v.get("volume_ratio", 0) or 0) - float(vol_ratio or 0)) <= 3.0]
            label = "мң мӮ¬ мЎ°кұҙ"
            if len(similar) < 2:
                similar = same_type
                label = "лҸҷмқј мӢ нҳё"
            wins = sum(1 for v in similar if v.get("pnl_pct", 0) > 0)
            win_rate = round(wins / len(similar) * 100)
            avg_pnl = round(sum(v.get("pnl_pct", 0) for v in similar) / len(similar), 1)
            best = max(similar, key=lambda x: x.get("pnl_pct", 0))
            worst = min(similar, key=lambda x: x.get("pnl_pct", 0))
            out["similar"] = {
                "label": label,
                "count": len(similar),
                "win_rate": win_rate,
                "avg_pnl": avg_pnl,
                "best_pnl": round(float(best.get("pnl_pct", 0) or 0), 1),
                "worst_pnl": round(float(worst.get("pnl_pct", 0) or 0), 1),
            }

        out["primary"] = out.get("similar") or out.get("same_stock") or {}
        return out if out.get("primary") else {}
    except Exception:
        return {}


def _build_similar_pattern_summary_block(stats: dict | None, top_exposed: bool = True) -> str:
    stats = dict(stats or {})
    primary = stats.get("primary") or {}
    if not primary:
        return ""
    prefix = "рҹ“ҡ <b>кіјкұ° мң мӮ¬нҢЁн„ҙ</b>" if top_exposed else "рҹ“ҡ мң мӮ¬нҢЁн„ҙ"
    return (
        f"{prefix}  {primary.get('label','мң мӮ¬ мЎ°кұҙ')} {int(primary.get('count',0) or 0)}кұҙ"
        f"  мҠ№лҘ  {int(primary.get('win_rate',0) or 0)}%"
        f"  нҸүк·  {float(primary.get('avg_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%"
    )


def _build_similar_pattern_detail_block(stats: dict | None) -> str:
    stats = dict(stats or {})
    if not stats:
        return ""
    lines = []
    same_stock = stats.get("same_stock") or {}
    if same_stock:
        s_wr = int(same_stock.get("win_rate", 0) or 0)
        s_emoji = "рҹ”ҙ" if s_wr >= 60 else ("рҹҹЎ" if s_wr >= 40 else "рҹ”ө")
        lines.append(
            f"  {s_emoji} <b>{same_stock.get('name','')} м „м Ғ</b>: {int(same_stock.get('count',0) or 0)}кұҙ "
            f"мҠ№лҘ  {s_wr}% нҸүк·  {float(same_stock.get('avg_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%"
            f" (мөңкі  {float(same_stock.get('best_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%)"
        )
    similar = stats.get("similar") or {}
    if similar:
        wr = int(similar.get("win_rate", 0) or 0)
        bar = "рҹ”ҙ" * max(1, wr // 20) if wr > 0 else ""
        lines.append(
            f"  {bar} {similar.get('label','мң мӮ¬ мЎ°кұҙ')} {int(similar.get('count',0) or 0)}кұҙ  мҠ№лҘ  {wr}%  нҸүк·  {float(similar.get('avg_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%"
            f"\n  мөңкі  {float(similar.get('best_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%  мөңм Җ {float(similar.get('worst_pnl',0.0) or 0.0):+.1f}%"
        )
    if not lines:
        return ""
    return "рҹ”Қ <b>кіјкұ° мң мӮ¬ нҢЁн„ҙ</b>\n" + "\n".join(lines)


def _apply_similar_pattern_score(score: int, reasons: list, code: str, signal_type: str,
                                 change_rate: float, vol_ratio: float,
                                 weight_mode: str = "strong") -> tuple[int, list, dict]:
    stats = _get_similar_pattern_stats(code, signal_type, change_rate, vol_ratio)
    primary = (stats or {}).get("primary") or {}
    if not primary:
        return score, reasons, {}

    sample = int(primary.get("count", 0) or 0)
    win_rate = float(primary.get("win_rate", 0) or 0)
    avg_pnl = float(primary.get("avg_pnl", 0) or 0)
    adj = 0

    if sample >= 10 and win_rate >= 70 and avg_pnl >= 2.0:
        adj = 6 if weight_mode == "strong" else 4 if weight_mode == "confirm" else 2
    elif sample >= 5 and win_rate >= 60 and avg_pnl >= 0.5:
        adj = 4 if weight_mode == "strong" else 3 if weight_mode == "confirm" else 2
    elif sample >= 5 and (win_rate <= 35 or avg_pnl <= -1.5):
        adj = -6 if weight_mode == "strong" else -4 if weight_mode == "confirm" else -2
    elif sample >= 3 and (win_rate < 45 and avg_pnl < 0):
        adj = -3 if weight_mode == "strong" else -2 if weight_mode == "confirm" else -1

    if adj != 0:
        score += adj
        reasons.append(
            f"рҹ“ҡ мң мӮ¬нҢЁн„ҙ н•ҷмҠө ліҙм • {adj:+d}м җ "
            f"({primary.get('label','мң мӮ¬ мЎ°кұҙ')} {sample}кұҙ / мҠ№лҘ  {int(win_rate)}% / нҸүк·  {avg_pnl:+.1f}%)"
        )
    return score, reasons, stats


# ============================================================
# v37.0 вҖ” рҹ“Ҡ мӨ‘м•ҷ мқҙл Ҙ мЎ°нҡҢ мӢңмҠӨн…ң (signal_log кё°л°ҳ)
# лӘЁл“  м•ҢлҰј/лёҢлҰ¬н•‘м—җм„ң кіјкұ° мң мӮ¬ мғҒнҷ© м°ёмЎ°
# ============================================================
_history_cache: dict = {"data": {}, "ts": 0}

def _load_signal_history() -> dict:
    """signal_log.json мәҗмӢң лЎңл“ң (5л¶„ TTL)"""
    if time.time() - _history_cache["ts"] < 300 and _history_cache["data"]:
        return _history_cache["data"]
    try:
        data = _read_json_locked(SIGNAL_LOG_FILE)
        if isinstance(data, dict):
            _normalize_signal_log_pnl_fields(data)
        _history_cache["data"] = data
        _history_cache["ts"] = time.time()
    except Exception:
        _history_cache["data"] = {}
    return _history_cache["data"]

def _get_completed_signals(data: dict = None) -> list:
    """мҷ„лЈҢлҗң мӢ нҳёл§Ң м¶”м¶ң (net_pnl_pct мҡ°м„ )"""
    if data is None:
        data = _load_signal_history()
    completed = []
    for v in data.values():
        if not isinstance(v, dict):
            continue
        if v.get("status") not in ("мҲҳмқө", "мҶҗмӢӨ", "ліём „"):
            continue
        _sync_record_pnl_fields(v)
        if _effective_pnl_pct(v, 0.0) == 0:
            continue
        completed.append(v)
    return completed

def _format_history_stats(records: list, label: str = "кіјкұ° мқҙл Ҙ") -> str:
    """кіөнҶө нҶөкі„ нҸ¬л§· (мөңмҶҢ 2кұҙ мқҙмғҒ)"""
    if len(records) < 2:
        return ""
    total  = len(records)
    wins   = sum(1 for r in records if r["pnl_pct"] > 0)
    avg    = round(sum(r["pnl_pct"] for r in records) / total, 1)
    wr     = round(wins / total * 100)
    emoji  = "рҹ”ҙ" if wr >= 60 else ("рҹҹЎ" if wr >= 40 else "рҹ”ө")
    return f"{emoji} {label}: {total}кұҙ мӨ‘ {wins}кұҙвҶ‘ ({wr}%) нҸүк· {avg:+.1f}%"

def _format_recent_examples(records: list, max_n: int = 3) -> str:
    """мөңк·ј мӮ¬лЎҖ нҸ¬л§·"""
    recent = sorted(records, key=lambda x: x.get("detect_date",""), reverse=True)[:max_n]
    parts = []
    for r in recent:
        d = r.get("detect_date", "")
        d_str = f"({d[4:6]}/{d[6:8]})" if d and len(d) == 8 else ""
        parts.append(f"{r.get('name','?')} {r['pnl_pct']:+.1f}%{d_str}")
    return " | ".join(parts) if parts else ""

def _format_capture_datetime_label(detected_at=None, detect_date: str = "", detect_time: str = "") -> str:
    """нҸ¬м°© мӢңк°Ғмқ„ мӮ¬мҡ©мһҗ н‘ңмӢңмҡ© л¬ёмһҗм—ҙлЎң м •лҰ¬н•ңлӢӨ."""
    try:
        if isinstance(detected_at, datetime):
            return detected_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
    except Exception:
        pass

    d = str(detect_date or "").strip()
    t = str(detect_time or "").strip()

    date_label = ""
    time_label = t
    if d:
        try:
            if len(d) == 8 and d.isdigit():
                date_label = datetime.strptime(d, "%Y%m%d").strftime("%Y-%m-%d")
            else:
                date_label = d
        except Exception:
            date_label = d

    if t:
        try:
            if len(t) >= 8:
                time_label = t[:8]
            elif len(t) >= 5:
                time_label = t[:5]
        except Exception:
            time_label = t

    if date_label and time_label:
        return f"{date_label} {time_label}"
    return date_label or time_label or "-"


def get_stock_track_record(code: str, name: str = "") -> str:
    """
    в‘  лҸҷмқј мў…лӘ©мқҳ кіјкұ° мӢ нҳё м „м Ғ.
    send_alert / DART / лёҢлҰ¬н•‘м—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©.
    """
    completed = _get_completed_signals()
    same_stock = [r for r in completed if r.get("code") == code]
    if len(same_stock) < 2:
        return ""
    stats = _format_history_stats(same_stock, f"{name or code} м „м Ғ")
    recent = _format_recent_examples(same_stock, 2)
    result = f"  {stats}"
    if recent:
        result += f"\n     {recent}"
    return result


def get_dart_keyword_history(code: str, name: str, keywords: list) -> str:
    """
    в‘Ў к°ҷмқҖ мў…лӘ©мқҳ мң мӮ¬ кіөмӢң нӣ„ кІ°кіј.
    DART run_dart_intradayм—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©.
    нӮӨмӣҢл“ң л§Өм№ӯ or лҸҷмқј мў…лӘ© м „м Ғ.
    """
    data = _load_signal_history()
    completed = _get_completed_signals(data)
    if not completed:
        return ""

    # 1мҲңмң„: к°ҷмқҖ мў…лӘ©мқҳ мҷ„лЈҢ мӢ нҳё
    same_stock = [r for r in completed if r.get("code") == code]

    # 2мҲңмң„: к°ҷмқҖ мў…лӘ© м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ к°ҷмқҖ м„№н„° + DART м—°кҙҖ мӢ нҳё
    if len(same_stock) < 2:
        # sector_themeм—җм„ң к°ҷмқҖ н…Ңл§Ҳ м°ҫкё°
        dart_kw_set = set(kw for kw in keywords if len(kw) >= 2)
        related = []
        for r in completed:
            theme = r.get("sector_theme", "")
            # кіөмӢң нӮӨмӣҢл“ңк°Җ feature_flagsм—җ л°ҳмҳҒлҗҗкұ°лӮҳ к°ҷмқҖ н…Ңл§Ҳл©ҙ л§Өм№ӯ
            if dart_kw_set and theme:
                for kw in dart_kw_set:
                    if kw in theme or theme in kw:
                        related.append(r)
                        break
        if len(related) >= 2:
            stats = _format_history_stats(related, "мң мӮ¬ кіөмӢң м„№н„°")
            return f"в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nрҹ“Ҡ {stats}"

    if len(same_stock) < 2:
        return ""

    stats = _format_history_stats(same_stock, f"{name} кіјкұ° кіөмӢң л°ҳмқ‘")
    recent = _format_recent_examples(same_stock, 2)
    result = f"в”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғв”Ғ\nрҹ“Ҡ {stats}"
    if recent:
        result += f"\n     {recent}"
    return result


def get_regime_history(regime: str) -> str:
    """
    в‘ў лҸҷмқј мӢңмһҘ көӯл©ҙм—җм„ңмқҳ кіјкұ° м „мІҙ мӢ нҳё мҠ№лҘ .
    мҳӨлІ„лӮҳмқҙнҠё мң„н—ҳ м•ҢлҰј / мһҘм „ лёҢлҰ¬н•‘м—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©.
    """
    completed = _get_completed_signals()
    if len(completed) < 5:
        return ""

    same_regime = [r for r in completed
                   if r.get("feature_flags", {}).get("regime") == regime
                   or r.get("regime") == regime]
    if len(same_regime) < 3:
        return ""

    # v40.0: crash/bear/normal/bull 4лӢЁкі„ нҶөмқј (кө¬ лӘ…м№ӯ нҳёнҷҳ мң м§Җ)
    regime_label = {
        "crash": "кёүлқҪмһҘ", "bear": "м•Ҫм„ёмһҘ", "normal": "ліҙнҶөмһҘ", "bull": "к°•м„ёмһҘ",
        # н•ҳмң„ нҳёнҷҳ (кё°мЎҙ лЎңк·ё)
        "crisis": "кёүлқҪмһҘ", "risk_off": "м•Ҫм„ёмһҘ", "euphoria": "к°•м„ёмһҘ", "panic": "кёүлқҪмһҘ",
    }
    label = regime_label.get(regime, regime)
    return _format_history_stats(same_regime, f"{label} көӯл©ҙ кіјкұ°")


def get_weekly_comparison(week_records: list) -> str:
    """
    в‘Ј мқҙлІҲ мЈј мӢӨм Ғ vs м—ӯлҢҖ нҸүк·  л№„көҗ.
    мЈјк°„ лҰ¬нҸ¬нҠём—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©.
    """
    completed = _get_completed_signals()
    if len(completed) < 10 or not week_records:
        return ""

    all_wr   = round(sum(1 for r in completed if r["pnl_pct"] > 0) / len(completed) * 100)
    all_avg  = round(sum(r["pnl_pct"] for r in completed) / len(completed), 1)

    w_pnls   = [r["pnl_pct"] for r in week_records]
    w_wr     = round(sum(1 for p in w_pnls if p > 0) / len(w_pnls) * 100)
    w_avg    = round(sum(w_pnls) / len(w_pnls), 1)

    wr_diff  = w_wr - all_wr
    avg_diff = round(w_avg - all_avg, 1)

    wr_icon  = "рҹ“Ҳ" if wr_diff > 0 else ("рҹ“ү" if wr_diff < 0 else "вһЎпёҸ")
    avg_icon = "рҹ“Ҳ" if avg_diff > 0 else ("рҹ“ү" if avg_diff < 0 else "вһЎпёҸ")

    return (f"\nрҹ“Ҡ <b>м—ӯлҢҖ лҢҖл№„</b>  (м „мІҙ {len(completed)}кұҙ)\n"
            f"  {wr_icon} мҠ№лҘ : мқҙлІҲмЈј {w_wr}% vs м—ӯлҢҖ {all_wr}%  ({wr_diff:+d}%p)\n"
            f"  {avg_icon} мҲҳмқө: мқҙлІҲмЈј {w_avg:+.1f}% vs м—ӯлҢҖ {all_avg:+.1f}%  ({avg_diff:+.1f}%p)")


def get_overnight_history() -> str:
    """
    в‘Ө мҳӨлІ„лӮҳмқҙнҠё ліҙмң  нӣ„ лӢӨмқҢлӮ  кІ°кіј нҶөкі„.
    мҳӨлІ„лӮҳмқҙнҠё мң„н—ҳ м•ҢлҰјм—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©.
    """
    completed = _get_completed_signals()
    if len(completed) < 5:
        return ""

    # мһҘ л§Ҳк°җ нӣ„ к°җм§Җлҗң мӢ нҳё (14мӢң мқҙнӣ„) лҳҗлҠ” м¶”м Ғ 2мқј мқҙмғҒ
    overnight = []
    for r in completed:
        t = r.get("detect_time", "09:00")
        try:
            if t >= "14:00" or (r.get("exit_date","") > r.get("detect_date","")):
                overnight.append(r)
        except Exception: pass

    if len(overnight) < 3:
        return ""

    return _format_history_stats(overnight, "мҳӨлІ„лӮҳмқҙнҠё ліҙмң ")


# ============================================================
# в‘Ұ кұ°лһҳлҹү 5мқј нҸүк·  лҢҖл№„ м •нҷ• кі„мӮ°
# ============================================================
_avg_volume_cache = {}

def get_avg_volume(code: str) -> int:
    cached = _avg_volume_cache.get(code)
    if cached and time.time() - cached["ts"] < 3600:
        return cached["avg_vol"]
    items = get_daily_data(code, 20)
    vols  = [i["vol"] for i in items if i["vol"]]
    avg   = int(sum(vols[-5:]) / len(vols[-5:])) if len(vols) >= 3 else 0
    _avg_volume_cache[code] = {"avg_vol": avg, "ts": time.time()}
    return avg

def get_real_volume_ratio(code: str, today_vol: int) -> float:
    avg = get_avg_volume(code)
    return round(today_vol / avg, 1) if avg and today_vol else 0.0

# ============================================================
# в‘§ ATR кё°л°ҳ лҸҷм Ғ мҶҗм ҲВ·лӘ©н‘ңк°Җ
# ============================================================
def get_atr(code: str) -> float:
    today = datetime.now().strftime("%Y%m%d")
    cached = _atr_cache.get(code)
    if cached and cached.get("date") == today:
        return cached["atr"]
    items = get_daily_data(code, 20)
    trs   = [i["high"] - i["low"] for i in items[-ATR_PERIOD:] if i["high"] and i["low"]]
    atr   = sum(trs) / len(trs) if trs else 0
    _atr_cache[code] = {"atr": atr, "date": today}
    return atr

def get_atr_regime_mult() -> float:
    """
    нҳ„мһ¬ мӢңмһҘ көӯл©ҙм—җ л”°лҘё ATR л°°мҲҳ л°ҳнҷҳ.
    нҠёл Ҳмқјл§Ғ мҠӨнғ‘ / м§„мһ… н—Ҳмҡ©лІ”мң„ / мһ¬м§„мһ… кё°мӨҖ л“ұм—җ кіөнҶө мӮ¬мҡ©.
      bull  вҶ’ 0.8  (нғҖмқҙнҠён•ҳкІҢ вҖ” мҲҳмқө л№ЁлҰ¬ нҷ•ліҙ)
      normalвҶ’ 1.2
      bear  вҶ’ 1.8  (м—¬мң мһҲкІҢ вҖ” л…ёмқҙмҰҲм—җ м•Ҳ н„ёлҰј)
      crash вҶ’ 2.5
    NXT лӢЁлҸ… мӢңк°„лҢҖл©ҙ м¶”к°Җ Г— 1.3 (ліҖлҸҷм„ұ лҶ’мқҢ)
    """
    regime_info = get_market_regime()
    regime      = regime_info.get("mode", "normal")
    nxt_only    = regime_info.get("nxt_only", False)
    base = {"bull": 0.8, "normal": 1.2, "bear": 1.8, "crash": 2.5}.get(regime, 1.2)
    return round(base * (1.3 if nxt_only else 1.0), 2)

def calc_atr_pct(code: str, price: int, fallback_pct: float = 2.0) -> float:
    """
    мў…лӘ© ATRмқ„ нҳ„мһ¬к°Җ лҢҖл№„ %лЎң л°ҳнҷҳ.
    ATR мЎ°нҡҢ мӢӨнҢЁ мӢң fallback_pct мӮ¬мҡ©.
    """
    try:
        atr = get_atr(code)
        if atr > 0 and price > 0:
            return round(atr / price * 100, 2)
    except Exception: pass
    return fallback_pct

def calc_trailing_stop(code: str, high_price: int) -> int:
    """
    нҠёл Ҳмқјл§Ғ мҠӨнғ‘ к°ҖкІ© кі„мӮ°.
    кі м җ - ATR Г— көӯл©ҙл°°мҲҳ (мөңмҶҢ -1.5%, мөңлҢҖ -8%)
    v41.61 #9: мў…лӘ©лі„ ATR ліҖлҸҷм„ұ кө¬к°„ ліҙм • м¶”к°Җ.
      м ҖліҖлҸҷ(ATR<1.5%) вҶ’ нҠёл Ҳмқјл§Ғ нғҖмқҙнҠё (л№ лҘё мқөм Ҳ ліҙнҳё)
      кі ліҖлҸҷ(ATR>4.0%) вҶ’ нҠёл Ҳмқјл§Ғ м—¬мң  (л…ёмқҙмҰҲ л°©м§Җ)
    """
    try:
        atr  = get_atr(code)
        mult = get_atr_regime_mult()
        if atr > 0:
            # v41.61: ліҖлҸҷм„ұ кө¬к°„ ліҙм •
            atr_pct = atr / high_price * 100 if high_price else 3.0
            if atr_pct < 1.5:
                mult = max(mult * 0.8, 0.6)    # м ҖліҖлҸҷ: лҚ” нғҖмқҙнҠё
            elif atr_pct > 4.0:
                mult = min(mult * 1.3, 3.5)    # кі ліҖлҸҷ: лҚ” м—¬мң 

            trail_gap = int(atr * mult)
            trail_pct = trail_gap / high_price * 100 if high_price else 3.0
            # мөңмҶҢ 1.5%, мөңлҢҖ 8% лІ”мң„ м ңн•ң
            trail_pct = max(1.5, min(trail_pct, 8.0))
            trail_gap = int(high_price * trail_pct / 100)
            return int((high_price - trail_gap) / 10) * 10
    except Exception: pass
    # fallback: кі м җ Г— 0.97
    return int(high_price * 0.97 / 10) * 10

def calc_reentry_bounce(code: str, price: int) -> float:
    """
    мҶҗм Ҳ нӣ„ мһ¬м§„мһ… л°ҳл“ұ кё°мӨҖ (%) кі„мӮ°.
    ATR Г— 0.5 л°°мҲҳ (мөңмҶҢ 1.5%, мөңлҢҖ 6.0%)
    """
    atr_pct = calc_atr_pct(code, price, fallback_pct=3.0)
    mult    = get_atr_regime_mult()
    bounce  = round(atr_pct * mult * 0.5, 1)
    return max(1.5, min(bounce, 6.0))

def calc_surge_escape_pct(code: str, price: int) -> float:
    """
    м§„мһ…к°Җ мғҒмҠ№мқҙнғҲ нҢҗлӢЁ кё°мӨҖ (%) вҖ” м§„мһ…к°ҖліҙлӢӨ мқҙ % мқҙмғҒ мҳӨлҘҙл©ҙ нҸ¬кё°.
    ATR Г— 3л°° (мөңмҶҢ 5%, мөңлҢҖ 15%)
    """
    atr_pct = calc_atr_pct(code, price, fallback_pct=3.0)
    mult    = get_atr_regime_mult()
    escape  = round(atr_pct * mult * 3.0, 1)
    return max(5.0, min(escape, 15.0))

def calc_partial_exit_min_pct(code: str, price: int) -> float:
    """
    л¶„н•  мІӯмӮ° нҠёлҰ¬кұ° мөңмҶҢ мҲҳмқөлҘ  (%) вҖ” мқҙ мқҙмғҒ мҲҳмқөмқј л•Ңл§Ң л¶„н•  мІӯмӮ° м•ҢлҰј.
    ATR Г— 1л°° (мөңмҶҢ 1.5%, мөңлҢҖ 5.0%)
    v41.61: л Ҳм§җлі„ л°°мҲҳ м Ғмҡ© вҖ” bullмқҙл©ҙ мқјм°Қ мқөм Ҳ, bear/crashл©ҙ м—¬мң .
    """
    atr_pct = calc_atr_pct(code, price, fallback_pct=2.0)
    base = max(1.5, min(round(atr_pct, 1), 5.0))
    regime_mult = get_regime_partial_exit_mult()
    return max(1.0, min(round(base * regime_mult, 1), 7.0))

def calc_stop_target(code: str, entry: int, signal_type: str | None = None) -> tuple:
    """
    мҶҗм Ҳ/лӘ©н‘ңк°Җ кі„мӮ° вҖ” v41.61: calc_dynamic_stop_targetмңјлЎң мң„мһ„.
    кё°мЎҙ нҳём¶ңл¶Җ нҳёнҷҳ: signal_type лҜём§Җм • мӢң н‘ңмӨҖ л°°мҲҳ м Ғмҡ©.
    л°ҳнҷҳ: (stop, target, stop_pct, target_pct, atr_used)
    """
    return calc_dynamic_stop_target(code, entry, signal_type=signal_type)

# ============================================================
# в‘Ё м „мқј мғҒн•ңк°Җ мІҙнҒ¬
# ============================================================
_prev_upper_cache = {}

def was_upper_limit_yesterday(code: str) -> bool:
    cached = _prev_upper_cache.get(code)
    if cached and time.time() - cached["ts"] < 3600:
        return cached["is_upper"]
    items    = get_daily_data(code, 10)
    is_upper = False
    if len(items) >= 2:
        prev     = items[-2]
        prev_o   = prev["open"] or prev["close"]
        chg      = (prev["close"] - prev_o) / prev_o * 100 if prev_o else 0
        is_upper = chg >= 29.0
    _prev_upper_cache[code] = {"is_upper": is_upper, "ts": time.time()}
    return is_upper

# ============================================================
# в‘© мәҗмӢң мҙҲкё°нҷ”
# ============================================================
# ============================================================
# рҹ’ҫ мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—… мӢңмҠӨн…ң
# ============================================================
_last_backup_ts: float = 0
_gist_id_runtime: str  = GITHUB_GIST_ID   # лҹ°нғҖмһ„ мӨ‘ мғқм„ұлҗң Gist ID ліҙкҙҖ

def backup_to_gist() -> bool:
    """
    нҳ„мһ¬ stock_alert.pyлҘј GitHub Gistм—җ мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—…
    - GITHUB_GIST_ID мһҲмңјл©ҙ кё°мЎҙ Gist м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠё (PATCH)
    - м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ мғҲ Gist мғқм„ұ (POST) вҶ’ IDлҘј _gist_id_runtimeм—җ м ҖмһҘ
    л°ҳнҷҳ: м„ұкіө м—¬л¶Җ
    """
    global _gist_id_runtime
    if not GITHUB_GIST_TOKEN:
        return False
    try:
        script_path = os.path.abspath(__file__)
        with open(script_path, "r", encoding="utf-8") as f:
            code = f.read()
        ts_str   = datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M")
        filename = f"stock_alert_{BOT_VERSION}.py"
        headers  = {
            "Authorization": f"token {GITHUB_GIST_TOKEN}",
            "Accept": "application/vnd.github+json",
        }
        payload = {
            "description": f"мЈјмӢқ кёүл“ұ м•ҢлҰј лҙҮ {BOT_VERSION} вҖ” л°ұм—… {ts_str}",
            "public": False,
            "files": {filename: {"content": code}},
        }
        if _gist_id_runtime:
            # кё°мЎҙ Gist м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠё
            resp = requests.patch(
                f"https://api.github.com/gists/{_gist_id_runtime}",
                json=payload, headers=headers, timeout=20
            )
        else:
            # мғҲ Gist мғқм„ұ
            resp = requests.post(
                "https://api.github.com/gists",
                json=payload, headers=headers, timeout=20
            )
            if resp.status_code in (200, 201):
                _gist_id_runtime = resp.json().get("id", "")
                print(f"  рҹ’ҫ мғҲ Gist мғқм„ұ: {_gist_id_runtime}")

        ok = resp.status_code in (200, 201)
        if ok:
            print(f"  рҹ’ҫ Gist л°ұм—… мҷ„лЈҢ: {BOT_VERSION}  {ts_str}")
        else:
            print(f"  вҡ пёҸ Gist л°ұм—… мӢӨнҢЁ: {resp.status_code}")
        return ok
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"  вҡ пёҸ Gist л°ұм—… мҳӨлҘҳ: {e}")
        return False

def _default_auto_backup_state() -> dict:
    return {
        "last_backup_date": "",
        "telegram_message_ids": [],
    }

def _load_auto_backup_state() -> dict:
    state = _read_json_safe(AUTO_BACKUP_STATE_FILE, _default_auto_backup_state())
    if not isinstance(state, dict):
        return _default_auto_backup_state()
    mids = []
    raw_ids = state.get("telegram_message_ids", [])
    if isinstance(raw_ids, list):
        for mid in raw_ids:
            try:
                mid_int = int(mid)
                if mid_int > 0:
                    mids.append(mid_int)
            except Exception:
                continue
    return {
        "last_backup_date": str(state.get("last_backup_date", "") or ""),
        "telegram_message_ids": mids[-max(5, MAX_TELEGRAM_BACKUPS * 3):],
    }

def _save_auto_backup_state(state: dict) -> None:
    payload = _default_auto_backup_state()
    if isinstance(state, dict):
        payload["last_backup_date"] = str(state.get("last_backup_date", "") or "")
        mids = []
        raw_ids = state.get("telegram_message_ids", [])
        if isinstance(raw_ids, list):
            for mid in raw_ids:
                try:
                    mid_int = int(mid)
                    if mid_int > 0:
                        mids.append(mid_int)
                except Exception:
                    continue
        payload["telegram_message_ids"] = mids[-max(5, MAX_TELEGRAM_BACKUPS * 3):]
    try:
        _write_json_atomic(AUTO_BACKUP_STATE_FILE, payload, indent=2)
    except Exception:
        pass

def _prune_telegram_backup_messages(state: dict | None = None) -> dict:
    state = _load_auto_backup_state() if not isinstance(state, dict) else state
    keep_n = max(1, int(MAX_TELEGRAM_BACKUPS or 5))
    mids = list(state.get("telegram_message_ids", []) or [])
    if len(mids) <= keep_n:
        return state

    delete_ids = mids[:-keep_n]
    kept_ids = mids[-keep_n:]
    if TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN and TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID:
        for mid in delete_ids:
            try:
                _tg_request("deleteMessage", {"chat_id": TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID, "message_id": mid}, timeout=12)
            except Exception:
                pass

    state["telegram_message_ids"] = kept_ids
    _save_auto_backup_state(state)
    return state

def backup_to_telegram() -> bool:
    """
    нҳ„мһ¬ stock_alert.pyлҘј н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁмңјлЎң нҢҢмқј м „мҶЎ (л°ұм—…мҡ©)
    GitHub нҶ нҒ° м—Ҷмқ„ л•Ң лҢҖм•ҲмңјлЎң мӮ¬мҡ©
    мөңк·ј н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ л°ұм—…мқҖ MAX_TELEGRAM_BACKUPSк°ңл§Ң мң м§Җ
    """
    if not TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN or not TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID:
        return False
    try:
        script_path = os.path.abspath(__file__)
        ts_str = datetime.now().strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M")
        with open(script_path, "rb") as f:
            resp = _tg_http_request(
                "post",
                "sendDocument",
                data_payload={
                    "chat_id": TELEGRAM_CHAT_ID,
                    "caption": f"рҹ’ҫ мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—…  {BOT_VERSION}  {ts_str}",
                },
                files={"document": (f"stock_alert_{BOT_VERSION}_{datetime.now().strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M')}.py", f)},
                read_timeout=_TG_FILE_READ_TIMEOUT,
                attempts=2,
            )
        if resp is None:
            return False
        ok = resp.status_code == 200
        if ok:
            try:
                state = _load_auto_backup_state()
                res = resp.json() if resp.content else {}
                mid = int((res or {}).get("result", {}).get("message_id") or 0)
                if mid > 0:
                    state.setdefault("telegram_message_ids", []).append(mid)
                    state = _prune_telegram_backup_messages(state)
                else:
                    _save_auto_backup_state(state)
            except Exception:
                pass
            print(f"  рҹ’ҫ н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ нҢҢмқј л°ұм—… мҷ„лЈҢ: {ts_str}")
        else:
            print(f"  вҡ пёҸ н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ л°ұм—… мӢӨнҢЁ: {resp.status_code}")
        return ok
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"  вҡ пёҸ н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ л°ұм—… мҳӨлҘҳ: {e}")
        return False

def run_auto_backup(notify: bool = False):
    """
    мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—… мӢӨн–ү вҖ” Gist мҡ°м„ , м—Ҷмңјл©ҙ н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ нҢҢмқј м „мҶЎ
    notify=Trueл©ҙ н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁмңјлЎң л°ұм—… мҷ„лЈҢ л©”мӢңм§ҖлҸ„ м „мҶЎ
    н•ҳлЈЁ 1нҡҢк№Ңм§Җл§Ң мһҗлҸҷ мӢӨн–үн•ҳл©°, BACKUP_INTERVAL_HлҠ” мөңмҶҢ к°„кІ© м•Ҳм „мһҘм№ҳлЎң мӮ¬мҡ©
    """
    global _last_backup_ts
    now = time.time()
    state = _load_auto_backup_state()
    today = _now_kst().date().isoformat()
    if state.get("last_backup_date") == today:
        return   # к°ҷмқҖ лӮ  мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—… мҷ„лЈҢлҗЁ
    if now - _last_backup_ts < BACKUP_INTERVAL_H * 3600 - 60:
        return   # мөңмҶҢ к°„кІ© лҜёлӢ¬
    _last_backup_ts = now

    ok_gist = backup_to_gist()
    ok_tg   = False
    if not ok_gist:
        ok_tg = backup_to_telegram()

    if ok_gist or ok_tg:
        state = _load_auto_backup_state()
        state["last_backup_date"] = today
        _save_auto_backup_state(state)

    if notify and (ok_gist or ok_tg):
        method = "GitHub Gist" if ok_gist else "н…”л Ҳк·ёлһЁ нҢҢмқј"
        send(f"рҹ’ҫ <b>мһҗлҸҷ л°ұм—… мҷ„лЈҢ</b>  {BOT_VERSION}\n"
             f"рҹ“… {datetime.now().strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M')}\n"
             f"рҹ“Ұ л°©лІ•: {method}")

def _prune_cache(cache: dict, max_size: int = 200, ttl: int = 3600):
    """v37.0: мәҗмӢң нҒ¬кё° м ңн•ң + TTL л§ҢлЈҢ н•ӯлӘ© м ңкұ° (л©”лӘЁлҰ¬ лҲ„мҲҳ л°©м§Җ)"""
    if len(cache) <= max_size:
        return
    now = time.time()
    expired = [k for k, v in cache.items()
               if isinstance(v, dict) and now - v.get("ts", 0) > ttl]
    for k in expired:
        del cache[k]
    # м—¬м „нһҲ мҙҲкіјл©ҙ к°ҖмһҘ мҳӨлһҳлҗң н•ӯлӘ©л¶Җн„° м ңкұ°
    if len(cache) > max_size:
        sorted_keys = sorted(
            [k for k, v in cache.items() if isinstance(v, dict) and "ts" in v],
            key=lambda k: cache[k].get("ts", 0)
        )
        for k in sorted_keys[:len(cache) - max_size]:
            del cache[k]

def _prune_all_caches():
    """мһҘмӨ‘ мЈјкё°м ҒмңјлЎң нҳём¶ң вҖ” мәҗмӢң нҒ¬кё° м ңн•ң"""
    for c in (_daily_cache, _force_cache, _deep_news_cache, _nxt_cache,
              _sector_cache, _avg_volume_cache, _short_cache, _foreign_cache):
        _prune_cache(c, max_size=200, ttl=3600)

